title: Competition is heating up on Wall Street. Here are 4 things to watch as they report earnings.

Competition is heating up on Wall Street. Here are 4 things to watch as they report earnings.. From credit risks to AI, here's what experts are watching as banks, including JPMorgan and Goldman Sachs, prepare to report fourth-quarter earnings.. Matt Mawson/Getty Images
